Package simulation

Package that implements the stochastic simulation based on event, provided for extension depending of a population. The Pending Event Container (PEC) is implemented using a PriorityQueue and can also be reused for other types of simulation.
Author:
Pedro Mendes, Rui Livramento, Francisco Costa
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Events
    Abstract Class where an event of the simulation is defined (to be added in the PEC) All the events have the event time attribute in common, and so when the object of this class is created, the event time is schedule (for the given time).
    PEC
    Class that implements a Pending Event Container (PEC), where the Events are added and saved, in the correct order in a Priority Queue, and triggered.
    Simulation
    Abstract class where is define a Stochastic Simulation based on the event occurence.
